' Priority constants note
note bottom of AptPackageManager
    **Priority Constants**:
    - PRIORITY_VERY_HIGH: 90 (Brew)
    - PRIORITY_HIGH: 85 (Dnf, Winget)
    - PRIORITY_MEDIUM: 80 (Apt, Yum, Pacman)
    - PRIORITY_LOW: 70 (Choco)

    Higher priority selected when multiple available
end note

' Async execution note
note top of CommandExecutor
    **Async Execution Details**:
    - Uses tokio for non-blocking execution
    - Preserves shell operators (pipes, redirects)
    - Captures both stdout and stderr
    - Timeout handling (30 second default)
    - Exit code tracking for success/failure
    - Works with "original_input" for shell syntax
end note

